These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: malaysian, egyptian
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skateboarding, tennis
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, boat
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the egyptian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Nationality   | egyptian    | malaysian |
| Sport         | tennis | skateboarding    |
| Transport     | scooter     | boat      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, cola
There are 2 different nationalities: german, indian
The people use 2 different means of transport: snowmobile, boat
1. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
2. the german is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | cola  | milk   |
| Nationality   | indian | german  |
| Transport     | boat   | snowmobile |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: singing, hiking
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, disaster
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, tennis
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is in an even position##4
2. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Hobby         | singing   | hiking  |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | musical  |
| Sport         | skiing   | tennis |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
