The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: documentary, comedy
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, quad-bike
1. the person driving the van is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person eating kiwi is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Food          | kiwi | eggplant |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy   | documentary   |
| Transport     | quad-bike       | van      |

