.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
There 2 different types of food: pumpkin, peas
The people have 2 different jobs:  coach, police-officer
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skateboarding, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the coach##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
3. the person eating pumpkin is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | peas | pumpkin     |
| Job     | police-officer | coach |
| Sport   | snowboarding | skateboarding    |

 #################################

 
