.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-14::.
There 2 different types of food: lemon, banana
The people have 2 different hobbies: hiking, writing
2 different pets are kept: rat, snake
1. the owner of the snake is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person eating lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |
| Food    | banana | lemon  |
| Hobby   | writing | hiking |
| Pet     | rat  | snake     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: photography, video-games
There are 2 different nationalities: turkish, dutch
2 different pets are kept: frog, bird
1. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
2. the turkish is on the left of the dutch##1
3. the person who's hobby is photography is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Hobby         | video-games | photography |
| Nationality   | turkish     | dutch     |
| Pet           | bird          | frog     |

